|Proemio.~  ^Incipit XV' cantus prime cantice Comedie.~
In isto XV+o~ cantu adhuc prosequitur autor de tertio girone, de
quo in precedenti tractare incepit.  Tractat autem in isto cantu
de peccato sodomie, sed quia isto peccato clerici et layci
maculantur, ideo in isto cantu tractat de clericis et literatis.
In sequenti vero cantu tractat de laycis, et incipit secunda pars
istius gironis in principio istius cantus, ibi: <Ora cen porta
l'un de' duri margini>; et finit in XVII, ibi:
..TEXT:
<<<FORMATTING-OFF>>>
     Poco pi@u oltre vegio in su la rena
     gente sedere, etc.
..TEXT:
<<<FORMATTING-OFF>>>
                        (^Inf.~ XVII. 35-36)
..TEXT:
In isto XV cantu V comparationes {*vv. 4-6; 7-9; 17-19;
20-21; 121-122*}, V notabilia {*vv. 35-36; 64-66; 91-93; 94-96;
119-120*}, et unum vaticinium {*vv. 64-66*} continentur.
